metadata.description:
𝕹𝖆𝖒𝖊: Sister Freya - The Blood Gorged

𝕱𝖗𝖔𝖒: Warwick Manor

𝕮𝖍𝖗𝖔𝖓𝖎𝖈𝖑𝖊: Daugther of the Duke of Warwick Manor.
Her and her 3 sisters roam around the huge estate cackling and giggling.

These cries eco throughout the enormous manor and intensify them, keeping the villagers awake at night.
They lure unsuspecting ones with odd jobs, like gardening duty, carpentry fixes around the estate, maid positions and more.

When they are done having fun with their "food" they lock them in the Manor's dungeon and bleed them dry.

The blood is then bottled up like wine and labeled "Red Rose Sanguinis" which they partake in in fancy crystal glasses.

When angered they can turn into flies and they are armed with sickles that they are not afraid to use to entertain their sadistic humor.
